### PR #04: ResolvedPostCard & ResolvedFilters (Archive Aesthetics & ARIA)

#### 📝 Description
Implements two components extracted to `src/components/`:

1. **ResolvedPostCard.tsx** — Archive card with grayscale aesthetic (`grayscale-[0.5]`, `opacity-75`), hover reveals full color. Shows "Resolved" badge, item type badge, image, title, description, metadata, author.

2. **ResolvedFilters.tsx** — Search + category + date range filters. Uses **single-select** category model (unlike multi-select in active feed) because archive browsing is typically more focused.

**Accessibility (ARIA):**
- `aria-label` on search and date inputs
- `role="group"` and `aria-label="Filter by category"` on category pill container
- `aria-pressed` on category buttons
- All interactive elements have focus states (`focus:ring-2`)

